243
00:19:45,184 --> 00:19:47,846
Fourth of July picnic this Saturday.

244
00:19:47,920 --> 00:19:50,320
Bring the family.

245
00:19:50,389 --> 00:19:54,189
- Mandy, stop us.
- Mark time. March.

246
00:19:54,259 --> 00:19:57,558
- Who is that?
- I don't know.

247
00:19:57,629 --> 00:20:00,530
Not from around here.
Move us.

248
00:20:00,599 --> 00:20:02,692
Forward, march.

249
00:20:02,768 --> 00:20:05,066
Fourth of July picnic this Saturday.

250
00:20:05,137 --> 00:20:08,163
Music and games.
