268
00:21:12,638 --> 00:21:16,438
Ahem. Hi. I'm the new office girl.

269
00:21:17,509 --> 00:21:19,500
You're Lilly's daughter?

270
00:21:19,578 --> 00:21:24,948
It's a pleasure to meet you.
I am Istegui Argitalexei Sarronainda.

271
00:21:26,184 --> 00:21:29,119
- But you can call me Izzy.
- Mm.

272
00:21:29,187 --> 00:21:31,587
- Better.
- And you?

273
00:21:31,657 --> 00:21:34,421
