Ethan, Sam, this is Rachel, my...

299
00:23:18,029 --> 00:23:19,189
granddaughter.

300
00:23:19,264 --> 00:23:22,233
- Do we have to like her?
- How old is she?

301
00:23:22,300 --> 00:23:24,894
