302
00:23:25,537 --> 00:23:28,700
I was just asking a question.

303
00:23:32,444 --> 00:23:34,503
You could offer us some.

304
00:23:34,579 --> 00:23:36,911
The kids are thirsty, too.

305
00:23:38,283 --> 00:23:40,717
Want a sip?

306
00:23:40,786 --> 00:23:43,880
I gotta finish here.

307
