332
00:25:45,977 --> 00:25:48,275
Happy?

333
00:25:53,919 --> 00:25:57,013
Paula Richards,
Rachel Wilcox my granddaughter.

334
00:25:57,088 --> 00:25:58,282
Mm.

335
00:25:58,356 --> 00:26:01,917
Georgia's been so excited about your visit.

336
00:26:03,895 --> 00:26:05,954
What now, Grandma?

337
00:26:06,031 --> 00:26:08,397
You can take it out.
Grab a chair.

338
00:26:08,833 --> 00:26:11,199
Thanks.

339
00:26:11,770 --> 00:26:14,739
(Rachel spits and coughs)

340
00:26:18,543 --> 00:26:19,567
Hey.

341
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:24,344
