May I be excused?

342
00:26:24,416 --> 00:26:26,077
Yeah.

343
00:26:27,452 --> 00:26:31,786
Would you go out and get us some ice cream?
There's money in the jar.

344
00:26:31,856 --> 00:26:36,816
