351
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:19,497
Please, don't shoot a dog.
I'd have to deal with that.

352
00:27:19,571 --> 00:27:23,234
You'll be all right soon.
Bring a cushion to the barbecue, though.

353
00:27:23,308 --> 00:27:26,800
- The peeing lady's back.
- Every week.

354
00:27:26,878 --> 00:27:30,507
My... Georgia wants me to help her out for the
Fourth of July barbecue tomorrow,

355
00:27:30,582 --> 00:27:32,641
so I'm gonna take off.

356
00:27:32,717 --> 00:27:36,278
First, there's some gauze in my office.
Will you bring that to me?

357
00:27:36,354 --> 00:27:39,721
- Yeah. Sorry.
- That should do.

358
00:27:40,458 --> 00:27:41,652
(man) All right.

359
00:27:44,462 --> 00:27:49,331
Is it in there? Harold, can you
