368
00:28:19,230 --> 00:28:21,221
(band plays new tune)

369
00:28:25,236 --> 00:28:28,501
- Peach, cherry or apple?
- Which one would you like, Troy?

370
00:28:28,573 --> 00:28:32,168
- I'll try the peach.
- Yeah!

371
00:28:32,243 --> 00:28:34,404
(vendor) Hamburgers, hot dogs!

372
00:28:34,479 --> 00:28:37,937
Mrs. Seymoure,
is the music too loud for you?

373
00:28:38,016 --> 00:28:40,712
You wanna move back, over...?
No?

374
00:28:41,653 --> 00:28:42,847
(woman) Hi, Bonnie.

375
00:28:42,921 --> 00:28:44,912
