377
00:28:47,992 --> 00:28:50,187
(man yells)

378
00:28:50,261 --> 00:28:52,252
- See you later, Simon.
- Bye.

379
00:28:52,330 --> 00:28:54,321
She'd be cute for you.

380
00:28:54,399 --> 00:28:57,334
She just likes me
'cause I just neutered her dog.

381
00:28:57,402 --> 00:28:59,836
That's nice.

382
