400
00:30:16,314 --> 00:30:18,748
Anybody can do anything to anyone.

401
00:30:19,751 --> 00:30:23,346
Can't stop what's done to you.
Can only survive it.

402
00:30:23,421 --> 00:30:25,446
Oh, please.

403
00:30:25,523 --> 00:30:27,286
You're 17.

404
00:30:27,358 --> 00:30:32,796
