427
00:32:14,632 --> 00:32:19,467
Simon says you might be
going on a mission for the Mormons.

428
00:32:19,537 --> 00:32:23,098
Yeah. I'm looking forward to it.

429
00:32:23,174 --> 00:32:26,143
