01:36:09,697 --> 01:36:13,827
He tried to take away all the things
that would let you love me like a friend or a father.

1203
01:36:13,901 --> 01:36:16,699
This has everything to do with him.

1204
01:36:19,540 --> 01:36:25,843
This is about knowing the difference between
right and wrong, between the truth and a lie.

1205
01:36:25,913 --> 01:36:28,177
He took that from you.

1206
01:36:28,249 --> 01:36:32,185
And if you can't tell the difference,
then you can't trust anyone.

1207
01:36:34,789 --> 01:36:37,349
And if you can't trust, you can't love.

1208
01:36:41,896 --> 01:36:44,797
What's it like to be so sure of yourself?

1209
01:36:44,865 --> 01:36:46,958
It's good.

1210
01:36:51,572 --> 01:36:53,938
Tell me about your wife.

1211
01:36:54,008 --> 01:36:56,101
Describe it for me.

1212
01:37:00,681 --> 01:37:02,342
Describe what?

1213
01:37:03,751 --> 01:37:05,912
How you loved her.

1214
01:37:07,221 --> 01:37:12,989
When I touched her,
I felt the best part of me being touched.

1215
01:37:15,930 --> 01:37:19,024
It's just a different kind of love, Rachel.

1216
01:37:19,867 --> 01:37:22,734
Do you think you'll ever have it again?

1217
01:37:23,904 --> 01:37:25,371
No.

1218
01:37:26,407 --> 01:37:28,500
Maybe. I don't know.

1219
01:37:29,677 --> 01:37:31,508
Maybe.

1220
01:37:33,814 --> 01:37:36,612
Thanks. For saying no.

1221
01:37:43,090 --> 01:37:45,718
(dog barking)

1222
01:37:54,101 --> 01:37:56,035
Where's your car?

1223
01:37:56,103 --> 01:37:58,071
Around the corner.

1224
01:37:58,806 --> 01:38:00,535
For safety reasons.

1225
01:38:02,443 --> 01:38:06,072
If I could lock the windows and doors
and keep her from you, I would.

1226
01:38:06,146 --> 01:38:08,239
I'll wait for her right here.

1227
01:38:13,921 --> 01:38:16,014
You know I know.

1228
01:38:16,090 --> 01:38:18,558
Come on, Georgia.

1229
01:38:18,993 --> 01:38:23,555
I don't care what Rachel says. I know.
And that must eat at you.

1230
01:38:24,732 --> 01:38:27,826
Having something that disgusting, criminal,

1231
01:38:28,702 --> 01:38:31,762
known out here, exposed,
out in the open.

1232
01:38:34,408 --> 01:38:39,471
If my daughter wasn't in love with you,
I would kill you.

1233
