I'll call you when I get home.

1238
01:39:12,446 --> 01:39:15,677
I noticed the glass bedpan on your mantel.

1239
01:39:16,283 --> 01:39:18,342
Yeah, I found room for it.

1240
01:39:18,919 --> 01:39:20,477
Thank you.

1241
01:39:33,367 --> 01:39:35,494
Hey, boys.

1242
01:39:35,569 --> 01:39:37,901
Come say goodbye to Lilly.

1243
01:39:40,574 --> 01:39:42,132
- Bye.
- Bye, Lilly.

1244
01:39:42,209 --> 01:39:44,837
Goodbye. Goodbye.

1245
01:39:53,220 --> 01:39:54,983
(starts engine)

1246
01:40:10,137 --> 01:40:12,264
(knock on door)

1247
01:40:12,339 --> 01:40:14,705
- Who is it?
- (knocking)

1248
01:40:14,775 --> 01:40:16,834
Coming.

1249
01:40:19,913 --> 01:40:22,746
Why didn't you answer the phone?

1250
01:40:22,816 --> 01:40:24,647
I just woke up.

1251
01:40:24,718 --> 01:40:28,154
Simon's at work already.
Did they leave yet?

1252
01:40:31,658 --> 01:40:34,752
I thought I could let it go, but I can't.

1253
01:40:34,828 --> 01:40:37,422
Rachel, you lied to her.

1254
01:40:38,632 --> 01:40:42,466
I put together a puzzle
without looking at the box.

1255
01:40:42,536 --> 01:40:44,265
- Look at me.
- Why?

1256
01:40:44,338 --> 01:40:47,364
Look at me. You have to tell her the truth.

1257
01:40:48,442 --> 01:40:52,606
Simon says I don't know the difference
between the truth and a lie.

1258
01:40:52,679 --> 01:40:55,648
- Can a lie ever be right?
- No.

1259
01:40:57,217 --> 01:40:59,378
And what happens if I tell the truth?

1260
01:40:59,953 --> 01:41:02,444
We're gonna press criminal charges.

1261
01:41:02,523 --> 01:41:05,515
But it's gonna take the three of us.
Come on, get dressed.

1262
01:41:05,592 --> 01:41:08,425
- What makes you think we'll catch them?
- Well, we'll try.

1263
01:41:08,495 --> 01:41:11,328
Simon and Harlan are in the truck.
She gave me this for you.

1264
01:41:11,398 --> 01:41:13,593
- No, no. Go get dressed.
- OK.

1265
01:41:13,667 --> 01:41:15,464
You can read this on the way. Hurry.

1266
01:41:15,536 --> 01:41:20,564
- What makes you think she'll believe me now?
- We'll make her, you and I.

1267
