All right, I'm doing it! I'm pulling over!

1289
01:43:06,413 --> 01:43:08,381
Goddammit, Lilly.

1290
01:43:09,283 --> 01:43:10,910
Talk to me.

1291
01:43:12,553 --> 01:43:14,851
